###
### 2. Get all users (default pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### 3. Get all users with custom pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### 4. Get user by ID
